00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:54.980 align:middle line:90%
and Sensitivity to subtleties.

00:11:54.980 --> 00:11:56.950 align:middle line:10%
>> HSPs showed more activation--

00:11:56.950 --> 00:11:57.750 align:middle line:10%
>> Right.

00:11:57.750 --> 00:11:59.550 align:middle line:10%
>> Than the non-HSPs.

00:11:59.550 --> 00:12:03.570 align:middle line:10%
>> Of the four characteristics,
this strategy of processing

00:12:03.570 --> 00:12:07.700 align:middle line:10%
or reflecting on information
more deeply or elaborately is

00:12:07.700 --> 00:12:10.250 align:middle line:10%
most basic.

00:12:10.250 --> 00:12:12.390 align:middle line:10%
It's behind all the
sensitive behaviors

00:12:12.390 --> 00:12:15.390 align:middle line:10%
one sees in animals
